{"tid":2178304,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【救手足】係時候再力推制栽紅官同律政司班賤畜救手足","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T10:29:08.000Z","uid":26846,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a04a888aad6e88d4f943a472e42a4c8bc7321a4","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"//鄭紀航：被告持有48條索帶 判處5個月2星期監禁 不可保釋上訴//<br />\n//麵包師藏14吋棍六角匙囚九月 官：眾所周知可敲碎車窗拆欄//<br />\n<br />\n紅官有幾出色我都唔再係度複述，但請唔好唔記得仲有一班律政司賤畜，<br />\n依班人明知好多都係無得告or生豬肉案，但仍然不停諗d罪名去入手足，<br />\n<br />\n以下真人真事，我係舊post開過<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n有次我去聽審，手足想保釋，條仆街檢控官話手足屋企有幾個豬咀，<br />\n所以佢係明顯既極端份子，唔應該比佢保釋，為左唔比手足保釋，<br />\n咩垃圾理由都用盡，事後佢地成班人離開法院，<br />\n仲好開心係度談笑風生，有講有笑，好似落左老蘭咁，<br />\n依班人搞死手足對佢地黎講就同整死隻''甲由''，或者摘走朵花一樣咁平常，<br />\n最心寒既就係依班人唔係d咩死老野，而係睇落去都2字頭3字頭既後生，<br />\n而佢地絕對唔介意踩住手足屍體上位，因為愈多屍體將來佢地就企得愈高。<br />\n殺人放火金腰帶，修橋補路無屍骸。<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">依班律政司賤畜救同紅官配合就不停送d手足入坐，<br />\n我地現時無能力對付佢地，但我地係好應該大力推制栽依班司法系統既仆街，因為除左黑警外最多鮮血既就係依班人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">你知唔知幾多手足最後唔洗入獄，但個心永遠離唔開個監牢？<br />\n你知唔知幾多手足既家庭因為咁支離破碎？<br />\n你知唔知幾多手足每日受恐懼既折磨？</span><br />\n<br />\n同場加映：出色紅官系列<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1987546/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1987546/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"94f84fd52bcfe3bc938323787bedc9b4a34c4ee6","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82717bfe28353f3a386ca5221b690ab7e6ca67ea","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac4e1b20d4738627aef17fba604fd11afd2d9d9","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ed606cda6b6bf224aa03d589de30fa5bc0cdd4","tid":2178304,"uid":255789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4cb73993ca95a029e47db14dfc9d16a4d1de59e5","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126f6c04285964061bb550f0e2e0850b131f0709","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3541050b804e73a0d9de977d8550fd328800022f","tid":2178304,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"257df061c83b04f147bf1cefc67fe9f0a4c7c158","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a035634e5fcd6b74ba0c4b321db7bb0f42eef64","tid":2178304,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}